{"tid":878262,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[社會問題]大家覺得快餐店霸位係可唔可以接受？","createTime":"2018-10-27T03:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T10:56:57.000Z","uid":21749,"like":275,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1614bd9b7302341934c570dceedbed055f55c329","tid":878262,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"霸位係指你係兩個人或以上既情況去自由揀位坐既餐廳(例: 吉野家,大快活)食野，留低一個人去霸位而其他人就買野食。<br />\n<br />\n正評: 合理<br />\n負評: 不合理<br />\n<br />\n歡迎自由討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4b070585008f4b3908a4520cbfa9bc80f98ba7","tid":878262,"uid":21749,"like":3,"dislike":112,"score":-109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"我先發表一下<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得係不合理既，最主要係因為會造成有人有野食但係無位坐，有人有位坐又唔係真係食緊野，資源錯配。<br />\n<br />\n有人同我討論我先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28d963be2df314a7f1b7403b6fcd8be28b97ba6","tid":878262,"uid":71237,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"樓主你一個人去食飯應該唔難搵位呀"},{"pid":"0492a5e3e39df71d77418bbf7aa540a2ba24ab9f","tid":878262,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8b9d74619160b33431580427fbe88cea78f708f","tid":878262,"uid":7763,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"樓豬係慘啲既<br />\n一個人食冇人幫佢霸位<br />\n<br />\n幫你負一負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c52e2791c2d0867cc2715c78dd34a1a989fe00d","tid":878262,"uid":23087,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"歸根到底 香港太多人"},{"pid":"45f667359533f98749cbb658cfa60dd8504650cb","tid":878262,"uid":60917,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"dc4b070585008f4b3908a4520cbfa9bc80f98ba7","tid":878262,"uid":21749,"like":3,"dislike":112,"score":-109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"我先發表一下<br 